title: MORTAL KOMBAT (2021) Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment: Wondering which MORTAL KOMBAT reigns SUPREME? Check out my video on the BIG Differences Between Both Versions: https://youtu.be/nsvEWlbTCGE
I like how they actually had to learn to unlock their powers and also show how they unlocked them instead of them just being able to use their powers
Sub-Zero was amazing in this movie. 🥶
I loved it when Shang Tsung said, "Death Is just another portal." That was my favorite line in the whole movie.
One thing everyone will definitely agree. As another addition to a Mortal Kombat movie adaptation, It's way better than Annihilation.
